            <p class="ml25">
                Is your company a FAA approved Repair Station?
            </p>
            <ul class="ml75">
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46318_70921 /> Yes</b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46318_70922 /> No</b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46318_70923 /> N/A</b> - Work will be performed outside the US by employees not recruited within the US, District of Columbia, Puerto Rico, Northern Mariana Islands, American Samoa, Guam, US Virgin Islands and Wake Island </li>
                <li class="mt20"><b>If Yes, please provide your Federal Registration Number: </b>@ViewBag.Checkbox46318_Comment</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="ml25">
                Do you have a FAA approved Anti-Drug Program?
            </p>
            <ul class="ml75 hr">
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46319_Yes /> Yes </b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46319_No /> No </b></li>
                <li><b> If Yes, please provide your Anti-Drug Program Plan Number:	 </b>@ViewBag.Checkbox46319_Comment</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="ml25">
                Do you have a FAA approved Alcohol Misuse Prevention Program?
            </p>
            <ul class="ml75 hr">
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46320_Yes /> Yes </b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46320_No /> No </b></li>
                <li><b>If Yes, please provide your Alcohol Misuse Prevention Program Plan Number: </b>@ViewBag.Checkbox46320_Comment</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>
                <b>
                    61.&nbsp;<i>
                        <u>
                            Additional Supplier Comments
                        </u>
                    </i>
                </b>
            </h2>
            <p class="ml25">
                @ViewBag.Input46374
            </p>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align:center; font-size:21px"><i><u><b>Overall Certification</b></u></i></p>

        <p>Supplier hereby certifies the information presented here is true and correct and meets the intent and spirit of the statements made above.  This Certifications and Assessment shall apply to all solicitations, agreements, Purchase Orders, contracts, or subcontracts received from Honeywell-Aerospace, and shall be valid for the current calendar year.  If any changes to the above occur, supplier will immediately notify their Honeywell-Aerospace Sourcing or Procurement representative, in writing, regarding its change in status.</p>
        <p>
            <ul class="ml75 hr">
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46376_Yes /> Yes </b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox46376_No /> No </b></li>
                <li><b>If No, comment required: </b>@ViewBag.Checkbox46376_Comment</li>
            </ul>
        </p>

        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="1">
            <tr style="height:40px">
                <td style="font-size: 11px; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom:5px;">
                    NAME: @(ViewBag.signature == null ? "" : (ViewBag.signature.firstName + " " + ViewBag.signature.lastName))
                </td>
                <td style="font-size: 11px; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom:5px;">
                    SIGNATURE:  @(ViewBag.signature == null ? "" : ViewBag.signature.email)
                </td>
                <td style="font-size: 11px; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom:5px;">
                    DATE: @ViewBag.completeDate
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="height:40px">
                <td style="font-size: 11px; text-align: left; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom:5px;" colspan="3">
                    TITLE: @ViewBag.personTitle
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </FONT>
</body>
</html>







